 "title": "Ice cream – 3 ingredients",
 "excerpt": "I know it's winter and who wants to eat ice cream now? But with a warm chocolate sauce it stays a winner. You can dress up the ice cream with chocolate shavings, finely chopped biscuits or whatever else makes you smile. The ice cream is very creamy and should be taken out …",
