 "html": "<p>I know it's winter and who wants to eat ice cream now?  But with a warm chocolate sauce it stays a winner.  You can dress up the ice cream with chocolate shavings, finely chopped biscuits or whatever else makes you smile.  The ice cream is very creamy and should be taken out of the freezer about 30 minutes before you serve it.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-075.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1612\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 075\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-075-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>YOU'LL NEED:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>500 ml cream<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1601\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 001\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-001-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>1 tin condensed milk<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1604\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 010\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-010-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>5 ml vanilla essence <a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-007.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1603\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 007\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-007-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>or 2, 5 ml vanilla seeds<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1605\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 011\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-011-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOW:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>whisk the cream to soft peak stage<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1602\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 003\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-003-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>stir in the condensed milk</li>\n<li>stir in the vanilla<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-014.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1606\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 014\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-014-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>spoon into a bowl and place in the freezer<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-021.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1608\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 021\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-021-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>You can top the ice cream with chopped fruit, chocolate, nuts or anything you like.  Really quick and easy to make. And it's delicious &#8230;&#8230;..<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-077.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1610\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 26052014 077\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-26052014-077-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>"
}
